songs.title: Untitled Snippet (19/08/19)*
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus: Ari Lennox]
[?]
I'm standin' here callin' your name
[?]
You stay treatin' me the same
[?]
I'm goin' out of the way
[?], you stay

[Post-Chorus: JID]
Okay I'm losin' my brain when I be fuckin' with you
You want me to stay but you don't act like you do
As soon I walk away you start to act like a fool
Now tell me, what should I do?
Now tell me, what should I do?

[Verse 1: JID]
Woah, I been doin' what I have to do
I was never really mad at you
We should focus on the factuals
Actually this shit was magical
Actually I'm pretty mad at you
Now that I think I got the attitude
Y'all been goin' down crazy roads
Make a right at truth avenue
Pass passion, go down a few
This is madness you passed it
You glad 'cause you passed it
Run of the gas and you had me
Shawty we lost now, where are we?
Tell a nigga not to worry
Drivin' this like a Ferrari
Why you in such a hurry?
Could it be you are hurting, so you find the pieces tryna hurt me?
Lord have mercy in emergency
It's gon' take for me to [?]
Just so we can see it, take a breather
Hate the feeling, feeling so defeated
Say you wanna change but don't believe it
[?]


[Chorus: Ari Lennox]
[?]
I'm standin' here callin' your name
[?]
You stay treatin' me the same
[?]
I'm goin' out of the way
[?], you stay
